03:40.080 --> 03:45.080
neurogenesis, neuroplasticity, neurogeneration, neuroregeneration.

03:45.080 --> 03:50.480
Those are four separate forms of neuron enhancement.

03:50.480 --> 03:53.920
And we can see this now very clearly in vitro.

03:53.920 --> 03:55.680
We are involved in microdosing.

