06:47.240 --> 06:53.680
of stimulation for helping people with neurodegenerative diseases.

06:53.680 --> 06:57.320
Now it's not just diseases, it's age.

06:57.320 --> 06:58.960
New news to everyone.

06:58.960 --> 06:59.960
