07:05.320 --> 07:12.680
So there was a metric in microdose.me, and when we surveyed these thousands of people,

07:12.680 --> 07:15.360
there was a statistic that jumped out.

07:15.360 --> 07:21.000
Now it did not jump out with young people, you know, 20 to 55 year olds in that range,

07:21.000 --> 07:29.240
but 55 plus year olds, there was a startling result that caught our researchers by surprise.

07:29.240 --> 07:33.840
And when they did the analysis, there was a finger tapping test.

07:33.840 --> 07:38.680
How quickly can you tap the first two fingers in 10 seconds?

07:38.680 --> 07:43.400
So when you're young, you can do it really fast, when you get older, you do it slower.

07:43.400 --> 07:52.440
This is a test that is used for charting neurodegeneration with Alzheimer's patients, dementia, Parkinson's,

07:52.440 --> 07:54.120
traumatic brain injury.

07:54.120 --> 07:55.280
This is a common test.

07:55.280 --> 07:58.760
Many people listening to this have taken the tap test.

07:58.760 --> 08:06.880
So the startling result was with psilocybin in any form, by itself with psilocybin mushrooms,

08:06.880 --> 08:11.480
psilocybin with chocolate, psilocybin with anything else, nothing statistically increased

08:11.480 --> 08:17.320
the frequency of tapping in 55 plus year olds, but one formulation, and that was called

08:17.320 --> 08:18.600
the Stamets Stock.

08:18.600 --> 08:24.720
Psilocybin, niacin, lion's mane increased the tapping frequency of approximately 49 taps

08:24.720 --> 08:31.760
to 68 taps in 30 days relatively quickly, with a p value of significance of p equals

08:31.760 --> 08:33.320
0.004.

08:33.320 --> 08:38.400
That means one chance in 250 that it's just random noise.

08:38.400 --> 08:43.160
So there appears to be a quote, unquote, cause and effect.

08:43.160 --> 08:48.600
When we saw that result, then I thought, well, what's the mechanisms of action, the modes

08:48.600 --> 08:52.680
of action, neurologically what's happening?

08:52.680 --> 09:00.000
